import React from 'react';
import { Unstable_Grid2 as Grid, Box, Paper, Typography } from '@mui/material';

import CustomSelector from '../../components/Staffs/StaffsCreate/CustomSelector';
import InputTextField from '../../components/Staffs/StaffsCreate/InputTextField';

const StaffCreateMUi = () => {
  return (
    <Box component='form' autoComplete="off">
      <Paper sx={{
        p: 3,
        m: 4,
        width: '50rem',
        minWidth: '20rem',
      }} elevation={6}>
        <Box sx={{
          marginBottom: '25px',
          display: 'flex',
          justifyContent: 'center'
        }}>
          <Typography variant='h2' gutterBottom sx={{ fontSize: '2rem' }}>
          Στοιχεία Προσωπικού
          </Typography>
        </Box>
        <Grid direction="row"
          alignItems="center"
          justifyContent="center" container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <InputTextField isRequired={true} name='Όνομα'/>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <InputTextField isRequired={true} name='Επώνυμο' />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <InputTextField isRequired={true} name='ΑΣΜΑ' />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <CustomSelector items={['ΠΟΛΕΜΙΚΗ ΑΕΡΟΠΟΡΙΑ', 'ΣΤΡΑΤΟΣ ΞΗΡΑΣ', 'ΠΟΛΕΜΙΚΟ ΝΑΥΤΙΚΟ']}/>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <InputTextField isRequired={true} name='Ειδικότητα' />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <InputTextField isRequired={true} name='Βαθμός' />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <InputTextField isRequired={true} name='Κινητό Τηλέφωνο' />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <InputTextField isRequired={false} name='Υπηρεσιακό Τηλέφωνο' />
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Paper>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default StaffCreateMUi;
